{"data":{"page":{"id":"a8789fe4-298c-5652-bc48-97277a4d0d07","html":"<p class=\"align-center\">\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://www.yonococino.com/blog/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch website</a>\n</p>\n<p><span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/16c613711dee67600ea94c8547aab8c8/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/16c613711dee67600ea94c8547aab8c8/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/16c613711dee67600ea94c8547aab8c8/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n  </span></p>\n<p>As part of my involvement in the <a href=\"http://iweekend.org/en\">iWeekend event</a>, I helped to build the selected project: Yo No Cocino, an aggregator of restaurants and other food related businesses with an online ordering process and a delivery system.</p>\n<p>I helped to build the blog using Wordpress and a custom theme.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2009"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Yo no cocino","categories":"web wordpress ux design","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/56693f77153a26318225e3c4c7982794/d927d/logo.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/yonococino/","source":"work"}}